snippet: Iran tested the guided missile hours before its Parliament approved the generalities of the nuclear agreement reached with six world powers in July.
abstract: Iranian state news agency announces country tested new guided long-range ballistic missile hours before Parliament approved generalities of nuclear agreement reached in Vienna with six world powers; test may hav violated terms of agreement.
lead_paragraph: Iran tested the guided missile hours before its Parliament approved the generalities of the nuclear agreement reached with six world powers in July.
